# Exploration: od

## Rounds
  round 0: 318 isolated cumulative, 169 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 18/21 flags
  15 solo, 3 via combination
  3 additional error-differentiated
  1 behavioral aliases detected
  robustness: 19 robust, 0 moderate, 0 fragile

